head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths WILLICK, JEFFREY ALAN

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths WILLICK, JEFFREY ALAN

block.p: WILLICK-Jeffrey Alan. A memorial service will be held at Congregation Beth Am, 26790 Arastradero Road, Los Altos Hills, Calif. 94022, on Sunday, July 9, at 12 Noon. Donations for the family can be made to The Jeffrey Willick Memorial Fund, c/o Stanford Federal Credit Union, P.O. Box 10690, Palo Alto, CA 94303-0843.
